 don't think just EVERYBODY would say that to him. Also, Rikuo doesn't exactly have the best attitude. He tends to moan, whine, and make sarcastic remarks about everything.","like_count":6,"author_id":"UCa1rHhly5Rp4BOOQYZMGwCA","author":"@MatthewTheWolf2029","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/jundKPOaFvx2VOCr82J4kV9Uf6KTC3BxXBOmY6WyvDvFMuf2a9RBYfgkjP44nMwxlq9RBDFiqg=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@MatthewTheWolf2029","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"2 years ago","timestamp":1714435200,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"Ugyt7DXiMRiuELRhKYt4AaABAg.A0mjKPjgyMyAA5m1wd-Joe","parent":"Ugyt7DXiMRiuELRhKYt4AaABAg","text":"Idk. Rikuo still has that appeal and while he is a weenie especially in the third episode, dude is still capable of doing stuff and has that \"all alone\" story compared to everyone else who's just an idiot or a terrible guardian to Harry kinda.","like_count":2,"author_id":"UChdVNNxY24xxwFdSeY0uPcg","author":"@dnmstarsi","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/B8z5I1BJsDmbzy1uvekQgWdNV9M0mlXpACQ5QGlQ0y3qjd2DpB6HTqyua_GR4lRRfMXfxFweaA=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@dnmstarsi","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"1 year ago","timestamp":1745971200,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"Ugyt7DXiMRiuELRhKYt4AaABAg.A0mjKPjgyMyAA5xgIpjOmU","parent":"Ugyt7DXiMRiuELRhKYt4AaABAg.A0mjKPjgyMyAA5m1wd-Joe","text":" @dnmstarsi  Fair enough. Though Felicia is a good guardian to Harry since she was very close to him.","like_count":1,"author_id":"UCa1rHhly5Rp4BOOQYZMGwCA","author":"@MatthewTheWolf2029","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/jundKPOaFvx2VOCr82J4kV9Uf6KTC3BxXBOmY6WyvDvFMuf2a9RBYfgkjP44nMwxlq9RBDFiqg=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@MatthewTheWolf2029","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"1 year ago","timestamp"